{"tid":1928621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞總幹事挑戰BTS洗手捱轟","createTime":"2020-03-16T13:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T13:24:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"40857e237d3f76d7958fafab904291134e62d169","tid":1928621,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:20:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200316/OADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200316%2FOADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA%2F&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2BebZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=4fb8e8e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200316%2FOADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA%2F&h=6bb17c14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200316/OADQOWBFRT57UC32MB7GC6PBJA/</a><br />\n<br />\n世衞總幹事挑戰BTS洗手捱轟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200316/large/1584275120_9868.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200316%2Flarge%2F1584275120_9868.jpg&h=c0489c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBTS被點名參加洗手挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐全球，要預防中招戴口罩和勤洗手最為重要，而世界衞生組織（WHO）總幹事譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）因為多次在疫情上對中國多番維護及讚美而屢受批評，未知他是否想洗底，他近日就在其個人及WHO的官方twitter上發起「THE SAFEHANDS CHALLENGE（洗手挑戰）」活動，希望大眾要關注洗手的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞更拍片親自示範如何正確洗手，同時他亦邀請韓國人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS）、美國樂壇天后Katy Perry等一同參加洗手挑戰，不過他此舉卻繼續遭到網民炮轟，指他之前遲遲不肯宣佈疫情屬大流行，令各國戒備不足，最終令武漢肺炎擴散至全球。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：施洛冰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200316/large/1584275119_46ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200316%2Flarge%2F1584275119_46ec.jpg&h=ad725ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世界衞生組織總幹事譚德塞拍片示範如何正確洗手。"},{"pid":"41e696d816d0747ffc509a365039a81ff1c453c1","tid":1928621,"uid":35919,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:22:29.000Z","msg":"呢隻死力架點洗都唔會白㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97ef04685acd146f1785b0849e93f9cc21b576b","tid":1928621,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a803e3b82e8482223fe3d0dc1cc6816aeb5462","tid":1928621,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"好撚柒 冇人理佢"},{"pid":"ff33f766ff5fe328f4858a1ef4081d14f5c0ce12","tid":1928621,"uid":289708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"自己個朶都已經臭哂仲好意思搞埋呢啲PR野"}]}